# AnswerRequired
# ---
2.1.5 - 2012-11-27
 - Added possibility to require answers on survey questions.

2.1.4 - 2012-09-18
 - Updated Polish translation, thanks to Piotr Augustyniak!
# ---
 - Updated Polish translation, thanks to Pawel @ IB!

2.1.3 - 2012-03-23
 - Added Portugal Portuguese translation, thanks to Rui Francisco!

2.1.2 - 2012-02-22
 - 2012-02-22 Fixed bug#8238 - Unable to enter questions in Survey.
 - Added Brazilian Portuguese translation, thanks to Filipe Mordhorst!
 - Added Italian translation, thanks to Massimo Bianchi!

2.1.1 - 2012-02-14
 - First stable release for OTRS 3.1.x series.

2.1.beta4 - 2012-01-27
 - 2012-01-20 Fixed Bug#8130 - Editing of General Info on Master Survey on possible.

1.2.92 - 2011-02-18
 - 2011-02-16 Fixed Bug#6826 - Survey shows blank overview screen by database error.
 - 2011-02-11 Fixed Bug#6865 - Norwegian translation for survey module.

1.2.92 - 2011-02-04
 - 2011-02-02 Fixed Bug#6849 - Survey Emails are not sending correct content.
 - 2011-01-31 - Improved HTML view on SurveyZoom related to Bug#4784.
 - 2011-01-31 - Implemented - Show survey answered on read-only mode.
    http://otrsteam.ideascale.com/a/dtd/Show-survey-answered-on-read-only-mode./103470-10369.
 - 2011-01-25 Fixed bug #6746 - Survey beta 1 does not install with ITSM.

1.2.91 - 2011-01-21
 - Init release for OTRS 3.0.
 - Implemented bug #5973 - Improve Survey-Key invalid message when survey is answered once.
 - Implemented bug #4784 - no WYSIWYG editor available composing email text.
 - Fixed bug #6711 - Question up arrow doesn't works.
 - Fixed bug #6712 - Answer up arrow doesn't works.
 - Fixed bug #6714 - Stat Details shows just one answer for questions with more than one like Checkbox.

